videos.description: J.A. Adande says that even with Stephen Curry and Draymond Green not on their A-game, the Warriors can still rely on Klay Thompson, who scores 36 points against the Lakers in a 109-88 win to improve Golden State's record to 33-2.
videos.headline: Adande: Klay Thompson a luxury other team's don't have
